headline: Teledyne to Participate at the TD Cowen Aerospace & Defense Conference
summary: THOUSAND OAKS, Calif., February 11, 2025--Teledyne Technologies Incorporated (NYSE:TDY) today announced that George Bobb, President and Chief Operating Officer, and Jason VanWees, Vice Chairman, will present at the TD Cowen 46th Annual Aerospace & Defense Conference at the Ritz-Carlton – Pentagon City in Arlington, Va. on Thursday, February 13, at 9:15 a.m. Eastern Time.
